    "SMEs play a crucial role in driving innovation, yet they fail to adequately strategize their cybersecurity defense.",
    "One of the reasons for this oversight is underestimating the risks and impact of cyber attacks.",
    "There is often a misconception that cybercriminals only go after large, highprofile organizations.",
    "Unfortunately, this couldn't be further from the truth.",
    "Verizon's data breach investigation report [1] reveals that nearly 43% of cyber attacks are targeted at SMEs."
